title: Large 1BD Sunny Apartment w/ outdoor deck!
posting_body: ['This north facing 620 sq.', 'ft. apartment is light & bright and features a spacious deck for your private barbecues, alfresco dining, & sunsets.', 'The open concept kitchen and living space feature granite counter tops, a raised bar top, large windows, new carpet, and fresh painted walls.', 'The bedroom includes a closet and separate laundry room with washer/dryer and organizer.', 'The full bathroom has plenty of cabinet space & a tub shower.', 'Reserved, secure parking garage stalls available $125/month.', 'Heated, secure storage stalls available $100/month.', 'Pets- Dogs and cats welcome!', '$350 Deposit for 1 pet/ $500 for 2', 'NEIGHBORHOOD', 'Ravenna offers fantastic locally owned shops, bakeries, & restaurants including the 2018 James Beard Award wining “Best New Restaurant in America” Junebaby.', 'Third Place Books, community center, fitness/Pilates/yoga studios, fruit & vegetable stand, community pea-patch, & quiet parks are all a short walk from your door.', 'On bus lines 71 & 72 with easy access to I-5 & 520 Bridge.', 'To view other apartments available, please visit <URL>', 'Review Screening Requirements: <URL>', 'To set up a tour please reach out to Lisa @', 'show contact info']
